Be Impatient With Actions, Be Patience With The Results.
 Patience is a misunderstood word. In my opinion, it has been associated with mediocrity, or at least has been used as an excuse for mediocrity.
Because people are patient, the business they want to start should wait, the book they want to read can wait, the gym can wait, the trip can wait. Because they are patient, they can always spend time with their kids when they retire&hellip;
